criteria.driver_alignment:
Implement — ran quantitative scenarios comparing buyback, dividend, acquisition, debt reduction, and R&D to produce outcomes;  
Validate — performed sensitivity tests (worst-case buyback price, lower R&D ROI) and ad hoc scenarios (higher premium, 50% debt-funded) that show conditions altering buyback economics;  
Evolve/Reflect — synthesized a specific hybrid allocation and explicitly tied the recommendation to stakeholder impacts and governance risks (CEO incentives, ownership concentration, bondholder risk).
